csw.services.ccs

Class SingleStateMatcherActor

  • java.lang.Object
    • csw.services.ccs.SingleStateMatcherActor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging

    public class SingleStateMatcherActor
extends java.lang.Object
implements akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging
    Subscribes to the current state values of a single HCD through the CurrentStateReceiver and notifies the sender with the command status when the strea matches the demand state, or with an error status message if the given timeout expires.

    See props for a description of the arguments for the class and message that starts the match.
